data.description: Adorable classic tri-level townhome is ready for you to call it Home! The main level welcomes you home with a large living room and formal dining area. The slider opens to your own quaint backyard patio to enjoy the outdoors. This home features porcelain tile (that resembles hardwoods) throughout the living room, dining room, and kitchen! The cozy kitchen offers space for informal dining and opens to the lower level. The stairs and the upper level have laminate flooring throughout. The lowel level rec room features a wood burning fireplace for those chilly months. The lower level also includes a 3/4 bath and an additional room (with laundry closet) that can be used as another bedroom, an office, or full laundry room! You decide! No HOA with this cute home! The only thing missing is you! Call today for your showing.
